               <ab>
                  <date/>
               </ab>
               <p>
Saturday 2nd August 1806.    a fair morning.    the <name type="person" key="Field, Joseph and Reubin">two Fields</name> Sent on a head to hunt.    we delayed to dry our baggage.    the day warm. Some of the men dressed deer Skins, &amp;C.
</p>
            </sp>
