         <div type="entry">
            <sp who="pg">
               <speaker>Gass</speaker>
               <ab>
                  <date/>
               </ab>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Saturday 2nd.</hi>    This was a fine clear morning, and <name type="person" key="Lewis, Meriwether">Captain Lewis</name> thought it best to stay here to day also, and dry all our baggage, as it was become damp and wet. Two hunters<ref target="n37080210" n="10"/> were sent on in a canoe to hunt; and in the course of the day we got every thing dry and ready to set out the next morning.


</p>
            </sp>
